    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels for Model Risk Level 2. Six factors are appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. The CFD model is accepted for use in identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device, supporting the regulatory submission with the RH < 1 acceptance criterion relative to the predicate device.",
